OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA bright and
OL,6,Fsunny evening. Some low cloud and fog
OL,7,Fwill move in from the North Sea
OL,8,Fovernight and spread slowly westwards.
OL,9,FA warm night for most, cooler along
OL,10,Fthe coast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FLargely sunny and warm once
OL,13,Fany early morning cloud burns back.
OL,14,FCooler along the coast with cloud
OL,15,Flingering there, this could move
OL,16,Finland by evening as a northeasterly
OL,17,Fbreeze develops.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
