OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FLow
OL,6,Fcloud possible early Sunday before
OL,7,Fbrightening up. Dry and sunny by
OL,8,FMonday. Tuesday will be cloudy with
OL,9,Fpatchy light showers possible.
OL,10,FTemperatures remaining above average.
